OL,4,G2200FLowry: A Simple Man
OL,5,     GA ballet celebrating the
OL,6,     Gcentenary of the birth of artist
OL,7,     GLS Lowry, inspired by his
OL,8,     Gindustrial landscape paintings.
OL,9,     GStarring Christopher Gable and
OL,10,     GMoira Shearer. From 1987.
OL,11,G2300FCastles: Britain's Fortified
OL,12,     FHistory
OL,13,     GSam Willis looks at how castles
OL,14,     Gsurvived into the Tudor era. But
OL,15,     Gthese strategic seats of power
OL,16,     Ghad to become palaces to impress
OL,17,     Gmonarchs such as Elizabeth I.
